metadata.name: The Bus Stop
metadata.description:
The Bus Stop

✤ ✤ ✤

It's about love, about her, about us, about you and about time. It's about a journey, a visual story. She's a poppy. She's rooted in me.

"Through the blue summer days, I shall travel all the ways,
Pricked by the ears of maize, trampling the dew:
A dreamer, I will gaze, as underfoot the coolness plays.
I’ll let the evening breeze drench my head anew."
A.R.

✤ ✤ ✤

Artwork & music composition by Mannay (2023)
